## 3. Module: Students

### Endpoints

```
GET    /students                    List students
POST   /students                    Create student
POST   /students/bulk               Bulk import (CSV)
GET    /students/:studentId         Get student detail
PATCH  /students/:studentId         Update student
DELETE /students/:studentId         Archive student (soft delete)
GET    /students/:studentId/batches  Enrolled batches
GET    /students/:studentId/fees    Fee history
GET    /students/:studentId/attendance  Attendance summary
```

### GET /students

**Query Params:**
```
?page=1&pageSize=20
&search=Priya           (name or phone)
&batchId=b_xyz          (filter by batch)
&isArchived=false       (default: false)
&sortBy=name&sortOrder=asc
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "s_abc123",
      "name": "Priya Sharma",
      "phone": "9876543210",
      "parentPhone": "9123456789",
      "grade": "10th",
      "address": "Pune, MH",
      "isArchived": false,
      "activeBatches": ["Math Batch A", "Science Batch B"],
      "feeStatus": "pending",
      "attendancePercent": 87.5,
      "createdAt": "2026-01-15T00:00:00.000Z"
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "page": 1, "pageSize": 20, "total": 45, "totalPages": 3 }
}
```

### POST /students

**Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "Priya Sharma",
  "phone": "9876543210",
  "parentPhone": "9123456789",
  "grade": "10th",
  "address": "Pune, MH",
  "batchIds": ["b_xyz"]
}
```

**Response 201:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "s_abc123",
    "name": "Priya Sharma",
    "phone": "9876543210",
    "parentPhone": "9123456789",
    "grade": "10th",
    "address": "Pune, MH",
    "isArchived": false,
    "teacherId": "T_xyz123",
    "createdAt": "2026-03-21T18:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### POST /students/bulk

**Request:** `multipart/form-data`
```
file: students.csv     (columns: name, phone, parentPhone, grade, address, batchName)
batchId: b_xyz         (optional override)
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "imported": 28,
    "skipped": 2,
    "errors": [
      { "row": 5, "reason": "Invalid phone number: 123" },
      { "row": 12, "reason": "Duplicate phone: 9876543210" }
    ]
  }
}
```

### PATCH /students/:studentId

**Request (partial update):**
```json
{
  "phone": "9999888877",
  "grade": "11th"
}
```

### DELETE /students/:studentId

Soft deletes: sets `isArchived: true`. Returns `204 No Content`.

