## 4. Module: Batches

### Endpoints

```
GET    /batches                     List batches
POST   /batches                     Create batch
GET    /batches/:batchId            Batch detail + students
PATCH  /batches/:batchId            Update batch
DELETE /batches/:batchId            Archive batch
POST   /batches/:batchId/enroll     Enroll students
DELETE /batches/:batchId/enroll     Remove students
POST   /batches/:batchId/clone      Clone batch
```

### GET /batches

**Query Params:**
```
?status=active          (active | paused | closed | all)
&subject=Mathematics
&page=1&pageSize=20
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "b_xyz",
      "name": "Math Batch A",
      "subject": "Mathematics",
      "schedule": {
        "days": ["Monday", "Wednesday", "Friday"],
        "time": "16:00",
        "durationMinutes": 90
      },
      "feesPerMonth": 1500,
      "maxSeats": 30,
      "currentSeats": 22,
      "status": "active",
      "term": "2026-Q1",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "page": 1, "pageSize": 20, "total": 8, "totalPages": 1 }
}
```

### POST /batches

**Request:**
```json
{
  "name": "Math Batch A",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "schedule": {
    "days": ["Monday", "Wednesday", "Friday"],
    "time": "16:00",
    "durationMinutes": 90
  },
  "feesPerMonth": 1500,
  "maxSeats": 30,
  "term": "2026-Q1"
}
```

### GET /batches/:batchId

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "b_xyz",
    "name": "Math Batch A",
    "subject": "Mathematics",
    "schedule": { "days": ["Monday", "Wednesday", "Friday"], "time": "16:00", "durationMinutes": 90 },
    "feesPerMonth": 1500,
    "maxSeats": 30,
    "currentSeats": 22,
    "status": "active",
    "term": "2026-Q1",
    "students": [
      { "id": "s_abc123", "name": "Priya Sharma", "phone": "9876543210", "enrolledAt": "2026-01-10T00:00:00.000Z" }
    ]
  }
}
```

### POST /batches/:batchId/enroll

**Request:**
```json
{
  "studentIds": ["s_abc123", "s_def456"]
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "enrolled": 2,
    "errors": []
  }
}
```

### POST /batches/:batchId/clone

**Request:**
```json
{
  "newName": "Math Batch A — 2026-Q2",
  "term": "2026-Q2",
  "copyStudents": true
}
```

