## 5. Module: Attendance

### Endpoints

```
GET    /attendance/:batchId         Get attendance records
POST   /attendance/:batchId         Mark/submit attendance for a date
PATCH  /attendance/:batchId/:date   Update attendance (retroactive)
GET    /attendance/student/:studentId  Student attendance summary
GET    /attendance/:batchId/summary Monthly summary report
```

### GET /attendance/:batchId

**Query Params:**
```
?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-31    (date range, max 90 days)
&studentId=s_abc123               (optional: filter one student)
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "date": "2026-03-04",
      "batchId": "b_xyz",
      "records": {
        "s_abc123": "present",
        "s_def456": "absent",
        "s_ghi789": "holiday"
      },
      "markedAt": "2026-03-04T17:35:00.000Z"
    }
  ]
}
```

### POST /attendance/:batchId

**Request:**
```json
{
  "date": "2026-03-21",
  "records": {
    "s_abc123": "present",
    "s_def456": "absent",
    "s_ghi789": "present"
  }
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "date": "2026-03-21",
    "batchId": "b_xyz",
    "totalPresent": 2,
    "totalAbsent": 1,
    "markedAt": "2026-03-21T17:35:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### GET /attendance/:batchId/summary

**Query Params:** `?month=2026-03`

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "month": "2026-03",
    "batchId": "b_xyz",
    "totalClasses": 13,
    "students": [
      { "studentId": "s_abc123", "name": "Priya Sharma", "present": 11, "absent": 2, "percentage": 84.6 },
      { "studentId": "s_def456", "name": "Rahul Verma", "present": 13, "absent": 0, "percentage": 100 }
    ]
  }
}
```

