## 6. Module: Fees

### Endpoints

```
GET    /fees                         List fee records (with filters)
POST   /fees/generate                Bulk generate fee records for a batch
GET    /fees/:feeRecordId            Single fee record
PATCH  /fees/:feeRecordId/pay        Mark as fully paid
PATCH  /fees/:feeRecordId/partial    Record partial payment
DELETE /fees/:feeRecordId            Delete fee record (admin only)
GET    /fees/student/:studentId      Student full fee history
GET    /fees/batch/:batchId          Batch fee overview for a month
```

### GET /fees

**Query Params:**
```
?status=pending         (pending | partial | paid | overdue)
&batchId=b_xyz
&studentId=s_abc123
&month=2026-03
&page=1&pageSize=20
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": [
    {
      "id": "fr_mno789",
      "studentId": "s_abc123",
      "studentName": "Priya Sharma",
      "batchId": "b_xyz",
      "batchName": "Math Batch A",
      "amount": 1500,
      "paidAmount": 0,
      "balance": 1500,
      "dueDate": "2026-03-10",
      "month": "2026-03",
      "status": "overdue",
      "paymentMode": null,
      "paidAt": null,
      "memo": ""
    }
  ],
  "meta": { "page": 1, "pageSize": 20, "total": 18, "totalPages": 1 }
}
```

### POST /fees/generate

**Request:**
```json
{
  "batchId": "b_xyz",
  "month": "2026-04",
  "amount": 1500,
  "dueDate": "2026-04-10"
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "created": 22,
    "skipped": 0,
    "note": "Skipped students already have a record for 2026-04"
  }
}
```

### PATCH /fees/:feeRecordId/pay

**Request:**
```json
{
  "paymentMode": "upi",
  "paidAt": "2026-03-21T14:00:00.000Z",
  "memo": "UPI ref: 123456789"
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "fr_mno789",
    "status": "paid",
    "paidAmount": 1500,
    "balance": 0,
    "paymentMode": "upi",
    "paidAt": "2026-03-21T14:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### PATCH /fees/:feeRecordId/partial

**Request:**
```json
{
  "paidAmount": 750,
  "paymentMode": "cash",
  "memo": "Half payment received"
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "fr_mno789",
    "status": "partial",
    "amount": 1500,
    "paidAmount": 750,
    "balance": 750,
    "paymentMode": "cash"
  }
}
```

