## 7. Module: Notes

### Endpoints

```
GET    /notes                        List notes
POST   /notes/upload-url             Get signed URL for Firebase Storage upload
POST   /notes                        Save note metadata (after upload)
GET    /notes/:noteId                Note detail
DELETE /notes/:noteId                Delete note + storage object
```

### POST /notes/upload-url

**Request:**
```json
{
  "fileName": "chapter5-notes.pdf",
  "fileType": "application/pdf",
  "fileSize": 2048576
}
```

**Response 200:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "uploadUrl": "https://storage.googleapis.com/bucket/notes/T_xyz123/chapter5-notes.pdf?X-Goog-Signature=...",
    "storageKey": "notes/T_xyz123/chapter5-notes.pdf",
    "expiresAt": "2026-03-21T19:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### POST /notes

**Request:**
```json
{
  "title": "Chapter 5 — Trigonometry",
  "subject": "Mathematics",
  "batchId": "b_xyz",
  "storageKey": "notes/T_xyz123/chapter5-notes.pdf",
  "fileType": "application/pdf",
  "fileSizeBytes": 2048576
}
```

**Response 201:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "n_jkl321",
    "title": "Chapter 5 — Trigonometry",
    "subject": "Mathematics",
    "batchId": "b_xyz",
    "batchName": "Math Batch A",
    "storageUrl": "https://storage.googleapis.com/bucket/notes/T_xyz123/chapter5-notes.pdf",
    "fileType": "application/pdf",
    "fileSizeBytes": 2048576,
    "uploadedAt": "2026-03-21T18:00:00.000Z"
  }
}
```

### GET /notes

**Query Params:**
```
?batchId=b_xyz
&subject=Mathematics
&fileType=application/pdf
&page=1&pageSize=20
```

