## 8. Module: Announcements

### Endpoints

```
GET    /announcements                List announcements
POST   /announcements                Create announcement
GET    /announcements/:id            Single announcement
PATCH  /announcements/:id            Update announcement
PATCH  /announcements/:id/pin        Toggle pin
DELETE /announcements/:id            Delete
POST   /announcements/:id/send       Send via configured channels
```

### POST /announcements

**Request:**
```json
{
  "title": "Holiday Notice",
  "message": "Classes are suspended on 25-March due to Holi.",
  "targetBatchId": null,
  "channels": ["inapp", "whatsapp"],
  "scheduledAt": null
}
```

**Response 201:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "a_pqr654",
    "title": "Holiday Notice",
    "message": "Classes are suspended on 25-March due to Holi.",
    "targetBatchId": null,
    "targetBatchName": null,
    "channels": ["inapp", "whatsapp"],
    "isPinned": false,
    "status": "sent",
    "whatsappLinks": [
      "https://wa.me/919876543210?text=Holiday+Notice%3A+...",
      "https://wa.me/919123456789?text=Holiday+Notice%3A+..."
    ],
    "sentAt": "2026-03-21T18:00:00.000Z",
    "scheduledAt": null
  }
}
```

### GET /announcements

**Query Params:**
```
?batchId=b_xyz
&isPinned=true
&page=1&pageSize=20
```

